rComments: Learned a lot from this class. The transition to online learning was a bit unfortunate but I think Professor Doudak handled it very well. I wish I could take the next level of timber design with this professor. The depth of knowledge he has and he is willing to share is amazing.
Very knowledgeable prof. great communicator and helped us a lot to learn and succeed. the class teaches a lot of new and advanced material which could be tough at times but overall very enjoyable
One of the best professors in engineering. He keeps the students awake even on Friday afternoon.
Proff has an ability to explain a topic in depth and yet simplify it with an interdisciplinary point of view. He was always available when I needed him.
Great prof. the lectures were enjoyable and I learned a lot. Has the ability to take very complex subjects and deliver them in an easy and clear way
Great prof, learned a lot
Useful information and a good class overall.
thumbs up
Great professor and provides great feed back.
Textbook costs a lot, and its a must

You NEED to come to class since a lot of the material is explained better there. The course lends itself to self study but if you want to get a good grade and understand the material you better show up.
Best prof, just attend his class . His exams looks long and hard if you are not prepared, cares a lot for his students. The project was very helpful and I learned a lot in this class.
Exams are a bit hard but he prepares you well for it. Classes are very clear.
Amazing. He is clear and cares about his students. One of the best teachers in the CVG department. The assignments and the exams reflect the material taught.
Great prof! Material can be tough, but gives many examples

Great proff. I learned a lot in this class. Highly recommended.

Great prof, take him with confidence !

he is an amazing professor, makes you understand the concept thoroughly and always ready to help when you need help. if you dont understand in clas ask questions.
He's an amazing prof, made sure you understand, not know. I would take his class again.

Very helpful and inspirational. Loved this class.
he is the one.

He's the best prof I've had so far in my university career. Passionate, funny, and truly motivated to ensure students learn the material well. I'd take this course again just to have him teach me twice per week.
Just a great prof. Cares about the students.

Very helpful if you seek his help in office hours. Very interesting classes, and keeps class alert. Tough subject but he makes it look easy and interesting. Highly recommended.

Great professor, one of the best in uOttawa. Cares for student and is very helpful if you seek him. Relevant design examples and excellent use of design tools.

He is awesome, if by the time you take this class you are still undecided in which specialization to go, then by the end Structural is going to sound more and more interesting. Simply a joy to have. Enjoying Monday night lectures ? What is wrong with me!

Great

Great prof. practical examples and fair exams. engaging class with a great combination of theory and equation. Best text book in the curriculum. Very useful and well implemented in this class. great teacher. very helpful when you need extra explainations.
